Dr Soham is a thorough professional, and I would highly recommend him. He is very caring, and have followed up personally multiple times, and checked on me. He gave sufficient time to review my case, researched it to come up with the way he would go about, and was very meticulous with the whole process. Mine was a very complicated and delicate gum surgery, and I am extremely satisfied with the way he operated upon and during the follow up visits.
Thanks Dr Soham

With an eternal fear of dentists, I reached Picasso dental studio two weeks back with many dental concerns. Dr.Soham Chatterjee was very patient to address all my concerns and fears and started the treatment promptly. He explained all the steps of the treatment and how to maintain my dental health in great depth. The clinic itself is kept at a great condition and the staff is extremely professional. I have been to dentists before but this has been my best experience so far. Looking forward to continue my dental journey at Picasso.

I visited Dr. Soham's Picasso Dental Clinic last week for dental check up and gum bleeding issue, its a very good dental clinic in park street with the latest equipments, great facilities and looks like a studio. Upon arrival i was attended by a receptionist who quickly took the required information, and as soon as my turn came Dr. Soham did a thorough check up and understood my problem quickly, he is  young and intelligent dentist and knows his job very well and is very confident dentist to perform all the required surgeries. He also taught me the basics of keeping my tooth healthy, and gave me a free toothbrush. i came to know since long i was not taking care of my teeth but now i will be taking care of it. I am happy I went to Doctor Soham Chatterjee who is a great dentist and will recommend a must visit for any dental problem.
It was a wonderful experience and Dr.Soham treated my teeth problems veey calmly. He gave me appointment within 5 mins of calling him. Will definately recommend him for his great sevices

**** ****** ****** ** ******* *** most friendly doctor I have ever met.
Super clinic and very friendly staff.
Excellent after visits experience.
Would like every one with a dental issue to visit here.

I am a patient of Dr Soham for a while now, i wonder why I did not get myself to write a review earlier, my bad. I have got RCT done, extraction done and am in the process for a couple of implants.  I must say that in my 32 years of service i was not lucky enough to get painless dental treatment ever. Dr Soham is not only a thorough professional but also a gentle soul. He has a state of art dental studio and uses the latest techniques and dental materials prevalent in the world. The staff employed  in the studio is very professional and  courteous. I wish him and his team of expert doctors and staff a very fulfilling and a rewarding future. His team has brought smiles to numerous faces including mine. Kudos and thanks a ton. Highly highly recommended !!

*** ** *** **** ******* ** ******* Dr.Soham clearly explained the various options I had to get my front tooth issue rectified & let me choose the best option that suited my budget , time & overall outcome I wanted. 
He maintains very high standards in dentistry using only the best tools & products. I was made to feel completely at ease & the experience was painless. The results were fantastic,  I am super happy that now I can smile without being conscious of my teeth.

Soham isn’t only an expert but a compassionate human being. He eases you into procedures knowing very well that a visit to the dentist is always daunting. I had my teeth cleaned and the results are more than satisfactory. He even gave me a primer on how to brush, and what I need to do to ensure better gum health. 

I’d recommend visiting him.
